{
  "body": "I ran across the following bug when running p6doc:\nUse of Nil in string context  in block  at lib/Pod/To/Text.pm:24\n\nIt looks like the error is actually in Rakudo.\n\nFIX: In sub pod2text add some null strings; replace:\n        when Pod::Block::Comment {  }\n        when Pod::Config       {  }\nwith:\n        when Pod::Block::Comment { \"\" }\n        when Pod::Config       { \"\" }\n\nThis works for me and appears to pass the spec test.  I'm not sure if this is the correct fix, but it's one that appears to work for me.  :)\n",
